{"title":"MTA: MAAP Transit Apparel brings new style to your daily bike commute","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/09/mta-maap-transit-apparel-brings-new-style-to-your-daily-bike-commute/","date":1636474008000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"398\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature-800x398.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature-800x398.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature-297x148.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature-120x60.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature-768x383.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103550/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-feature.jpg 1313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277940\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>For those times you’re not out <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/17/maap-training-kit-fall-2021/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">training</a> or <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/01/maap-alt_road-collection-helps-take-the-road-less-traveled-w-durable-modular-apparel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">riding gravel</a>, MAAP has a new clothing range to consider. Calling it their first lifestyle collection, I this case MTA stands for MAAP Transit Apparel. Naturally, that means clothing that is designed to wear for your daily commute, but stylish enough that you won’t want to ditch it as soon as you get to your destination.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel cycling commuting\" width=\"1200\" height=\"811\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1-297x201.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1-800x541.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1-120x81.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103232/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-4_1-768x519.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>From what we’ve seen from MAAP so far, they focus heavily on style, quality, sustainability, and fit. The MTA line looks to follow those cues with Bluesigh certified materials. Designed around unisex sizing that ranges from XS-XXL, the line features four-way stretch material to work well on the bike and a casual cut that will blend in off the bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel \" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103245/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-9-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel rain jacket\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1-297x197.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1-800x530.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103218/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1_1-768x509.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>While there is certainly a lot of dark colors in the line, MAAP includes bright blocks of color to provide high visibility.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel high viz\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1-297x197.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1-800x530.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103227/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-3_1-768x509.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel down jacket\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1-297x197.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1-800x530.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103223/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-2_1-768x509.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>“The MAAP Transit Apparel collection was made by cyclists for cyclists. This collection is crafted from materials that are breathable, highly sweat wicking and antimicrobial. We’ve partnered with innovative product performance specialists like Primaloft®, Polartec® and Drirelease® on new fabrics to remove the guesswork from commuting, empowering riders to get from home to work and everywhere in between with confidence in their clothing choice”, said Darren Tabone, VP Product at MAAP</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"MAAP Transit Apparel \" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1-80x120.jpg 80w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09103215/MAAP-Transit-apparel-commuting-style-1-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/1